{"tid":2005694,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"與梁志祥同被「起底」 周浩鼎促警調查：禍不及妻兒","createTime":"2020-05-07T09:23:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-07T16:05:36.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"75a66b98e13efffce6c1b0d2375d89b4f30813fa","tid":2005694,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T09:23:01.000Z","msg":"民建聯立法會議員周浩鼎表示，昨晚有Telegram群組將他和妻子的身分證號碼等個人資料公開，已向警方報案，要求警方嚴肅跟進，盡快展開刑事調查，將起底者繩之於法。他嚴厲譴責有關惡行，又指強調「禍不及妻兒」，批評將其家人一同起底最為缺德。<br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員梁志祥說，自己的住址、電話、家人姓名等亦被公開，該黨元朗和屯門的社區主任也遭不同程度的起底。他強調違法者要受到應有懲罰，希望不要再作無聊和傷害他人的起底。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1765642/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E8%88%87%E6%A2%81%E5%BF%97%E7%A5%A5%E5%90%8C%E8%A2%AB-%E8%B5%B7%E5%BA%95-%E5%91%A8%E6%B5%A9%E9%BC%8E%E4%BF%83%E8%AD%A6%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-%E7%A6%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%8A%E5%A6%BB%E5%85%92</code></pre>"},{"pid":"8cb1879a2ea2201fd00b921a47ecc02b1888f21a","tid":2005694,"uid":31151,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T09:27:08.000Z","msg":"吓 佢地主人共產黨仲鐘意禍及妻兒喎 幾時同共產黨講禍不及妻兒？"},{"pid":"65112e6ea2fae07643736f3713bc18f38fc4b1e8","tid":2005694,"uid":54579,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T09:29:12.000Z","msg":"即係認自己闖左禍？"},{"pid":"d4a8c5d4b9cf518a4e068caa7e62f5ae586f3e43","tid":2005694,"uid":94828,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T09:29:41.000Z","msg":"睇錯羅志祥"},{"pid":"d47cf8710299244ed90d4b00c08d1588b5338b32","tid":2005694,"uid":269202,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T09:30:54.000Z","msg":"你地製造恐襲同多次帶黑黑鬧事<br />\n<br />\n照香港警察對付疑犯既標準對佢地就岩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一定要依法施政"},{"pid":"c44957dadd5d08f1dabcecd0e0a2f8bd245c9259","tid":2005694,"uid":335434,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T09:31:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191011/_2019101106394337973.jpg\" data-th